s=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"點解會有念珠菌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"甚麼是念珠菌陰道炎？<br />\n<br />\n念珠菌陰道炎常見於生育年齡婦女，是由於一種名為「白色念珠菌」的真菌(簡稱念珠菌)在陰道過度增生所致。<br />\n在正常的情況下，女性的陰道存有少量念珠菌，但當陰道的酸鹼度有所轉變時，使念珠菌的數量增多，婦女受念珠菌感染的機會便會提高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n念珠菌陰道炎是否需要接受治療？<br />\n<br />\n大部分婦女是沒有任何徵狀，毋須接受治療。"},{"pid":"9cd83d2d493b60989757a980c3927f43257f6f3f","tid":1803113,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c28abf2c0ba3f33d9e1ee1d056381cdf899b16c7","tid":1803113,"uid":181474,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"肯定係因為屌到鬆咗會噴屎先唔屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"妹妹點噴屎"},{"pid":"19ec16ce4632d300f3b8cb4ad34e5d1fb871c2e9","tid":1803113,"uid":168730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:38:08.000Z","msg":"波台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62416e8eb981bb38f33e8851ec6883dcfc6877f","tid":1803113,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6f60bc9156a8c0c17d0b4d3775bc99044868ab4","tid":1803113,"uid":41288,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"10e2e828e08a82169a8fb0a50a5a4e4d006482a2","tid":1803113,"uid":321977,"like":388,"dislike":2,"score":386,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<br />\n樓主新婚完無耐就有2個小朋友<br />\n建議樓主睇睇精神科，打少啲飛機唔好咁多幻想<br />\n兩個男人互射係無可能懷孕"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:28:48.000Z","msg":"笑撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkg